; Chain baseline: two independent visible request outputs are returned
; sequentially by the consumer.
REQ_START summary
  REQ_YIELD content
  SET_MODEL summary-model
  MSG_START
    ROLE_USR
    TXT_CHUNK Summarize the incident report in one paragraph.
  MSG_END
REQ_END


REQ_START risk
  REQ_YIELD content
  SET_MODEL risk-model
  MSG_START
    ROLE_USR
    TXT_CHUNK List the top three follow-up risks from the incident report.
  MSG_END
REQ_END
